---
title: Cal Smart Honey Chicken Breasts with Roasted Carrots and Garlicky Rice
description: Sweet and savoury meet in our honey-glazed chicken breasts with roasted carrots. Bold garlic, zesty green onions and sweet honey lighten up this swap on takeout.

